Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.33,0:22:39.00,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}不會向悲傷低頭的勇氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.47,0:22:45.25,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}為了保護珍貴的事物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.32,0:22:50.66,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}我相信自己的堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:56.52,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,50)}Saving our future  讓我們一同
